edical Services (EMS) spokesperson, Robert Mulaudzi, there are currently only 13 fire trucks in operation throughout the city. Considering that there are 31 fire stations all over Johannesburg, the situation is less than ideal. Any additional resources will surely be to the benefit of the residents of Johannesburg. IOL